title: Mini Ep 16: Caroline and Jackie Go Estate Sale Shopping

itunes:subtitle: And Caroline uses a fetal stethoscope on Jackie.
description:
Jackie and Caroline go to an estate sale and buy a fetal stethoscope and then Caroline uses it on Jackie. Jackie also learns WOMEN…can be doctors!
